@node Future "Future"


                            THE FUTURE



As you may have seen, WWSpell is a simple spelling checker. 
A lot of stuff can be improved and added, and these are my own 
suggestions, which I am probably working on as you read this.


 1. Check for big capitals after a dot (new sentence).

 2. Add a 'Suggest' option to suggest some well-spelled words.


Feel free to send me an e-mail with more possible improvements.


@endnode
